						<div class="postbody">Is your program waiting the proper amount of time to allow the PPU to stablize on bootup, before writing to any PPU registers? This is the absolute only thing I can think of that would cause weird glitches on the hardware, where it wouldn't on emulators.
<br />
<br />Then again, if this is the powerpak, it probably wouldn't matter... but it's all I've got. *shrugs*</div>

					
